com.adobe.aem.init.dogmatix.config

Class ModuleConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.aem.init.dogmatix.config.ModuleConfig

  • public class ModuleConfig
extends Object
    Module level configuration POJO A module is uniquely identified by its Class and URL. This implies that the same module can consume requests from 2 different URLs while still exhibiting separate handling behaviour.
    Author:
    vnagpal
